      "details": "Create org.jsoup.nodes.ElementChildSupport in the same package. Move the child element caching constants (childElsKey, childElsMod), the cachedChildren()/stashChildren()/childElementsList() implementations, NodeList inner class, and child-node indexing methods into ElementChildSupport as package-private static helpers that accept an Element argument or expose instance helpers. Leave small delegating methods in Element (e.g. childElementsList(), cachedChildren(), stashChildren()) that call ElementChildSupport so existing calls from other Element methods remain unchanged. Preserve usage of package-private fields (childNodes, attributes) by locating the new class in org.jsoup.nodes.",
